<p>
Dear User
</p>
<p>
This is to inform you that the status of sample
<%=@sample.code%> (your ref <%=@sample.userref%>) submitted by
<%="#{@sample.user.firstname} #{@sample.user.lastname}"%> 
has changed as follows:
</p>

<p>
<%="New Status: #{@sample.flag.name} (#{@sample.flag.description})"%>
</p>

<p>
<%="Feedback: #{@sample.feedback}"%>
</p>

<p>
<%="Old Status: #{@old_flag.name} (#{@old_flag.description})"%>
</p>

<p>
<%= link_to "Link to Full Sample Information", "#{sample_url(@sample, 
            :host => MAIL_HOST)}" %>
</p>

<% if ( @sample.flag.name =~ /(FAILED|WITHDRAWN|REFINEMENT COMPLETED)/i ) %>
<p>
    <%= "#{TERMINATION_MESSAGE}" %>
</p>
<% end %>

<p>
Copies of this email are sent to both sample submitters and their
research group leaders (where different).
</p>

<p>
Newcastle Crystallography Service
</p>
